name: Saddie be the Shark
description:
Saddie the Shark is really Sad as her home is been trashed by humans and the ocean has darkned due to all the trash floating over the ocean help her be happy by collecting as much as trash as you can.

Also stay away from the old ship wrecks that fall upon you they really hurt also if you get too low on health saddie will help you by providing health.

Don't forget to help the real chads Mr.Beast and Mark Rober and team who are helping the real saddie out there in ocean with #TeamSeas
